des:
With OS Home, you can experience a new way of controlling your smart home. For hands-free management of the air conditioner and other compatible Olimpia Splendid products, just ask and Alexa will do it for you. Here is a step-by-step guide:

1.Download the OS Home app from Google Play or the iOS App Store.
2.Start the app and register a new account (or login if you have already registered).
3.Turn on your Olimpia Splendid products and connect them with the OS Home app.
4.Important: you can rename the devices in the OS Home app. For example, if you rename the air conditioner to “Living room”, Echo will learn the new name after discovering the product (see step 7).
5.Enable “OS Home” skill, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
6.Ask Echo “Alexa, discover my devices” and wait until you received the “Discovery completed” message.
7.Try your Olimpia Splendid products using Echo and these example commands: 
Alexa, set the air conditioner to 26°C; 
Alexa, set the living room to heating mode; 
Alexa, turn the air purifier on; 
Alexa, turn the dehumidifier off.
